{"tid":732630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩命】直播生吞49條泥鰍","createTime":"2018-07-07T05:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T07:00:23.000Z","uid":84908,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d06e5835235ee0ccd0aebe7e7ba0f3e71d355d","tid":732630,"uid":84908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180707/58406405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180707%2F58406405&d=zrTRZ2mwaJxZQo0%2B%2FKHujdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=18eaa67f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180707%2F58406405&h=3d0081f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180707/58406405</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180706/large/1530884813_68e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180706%2Flarge%2F1530884813_68e3.jpg&h=7d58b58d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界難撈，如今做直播，也要搵命博。網上近日瘋傳一段短片，一名送外賣的男子利用空餘時間做直播，但想到自己只懂得送外賣，其他甚麼都不會，便決定在直播時表演生吞泥鰍。這名外賣小哥將49條活泥鰍全部都倒入紅酒中，在網友的歡呼下一口氣將這杯紅酒泥鰍喝完。結果...悲劇發生了！<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒並沒有交待，這名外賣小哥來自何處，以及何時在直播中表演這場生吞泥鰍，但就指他將這杯紅酒泥鰍喝完後，自己的胃相當難受，這些泥鰍在胃裏不停的翻滾，這讓小哥痛的在地上打滾。直播最後被迫終止，小哥則被緊急送到醫院去了。<br />\n至於這名外賣小哥的現況，則未見相關報道，但內媒記者不忘最後勸戒這名外賣小哥，「看來錢也不是那麼好賺的，還是老老實實的送外賣吧。」<br />\n<br />\n支那仔牛X死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b598af270ea7ed8ef85005f4dc9299f05854f0","tid":732630,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"sb"},{"pid":"79c99d2bd954e86d299665c4e5d4a4c15f88e0b4","tid":732630,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"死撚左未？？"},{"pid":"ba49e8a77bcdc6e4993e583ba39474338102c942","tid":732630,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會咬穿個胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}